"Kennedy" is a news panel show hosted by Kennedy Montgomery. Kennedy Montgomery is a libertarian that you may recognize from 90's MTV, Stossel, and the Independents.

Tonight Kennedy kicks the night off talking about Pope Francis and the fawning bipartisan procession.

Our party panel tonight conists of JEDIDIAH BILA, JOE DeVITO, and JAMIE. They continue to talk about the Pope. Rubio and Cruz quietly rise in recent polls, Lena Dunham interviews Hillary Clinton - unsurprisingly throws softballs.

CHARLIE LeDUFF is here to talk about the GOP and immigration.

POPE OR FICTION! Our panel answers a bunch of fact of fiction questions about the Pope.

Booze Traveler host JACK MAXWELL is in studio to talk about travelling and getting hammered. 

Nightcap. Mailbag.
